318
00:15:33,270 --> 00:15:34,320
That's a forged decree!

319
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:41,440
Wu Guangming, receive the decree.

320
00:15:47,550 --> 00:15:48,790
By the Mandate of Heaven,

321
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:49,960
His Majesty decrees:

322
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:52,320
Wu Guangming, Chairman of the MAA,

