329
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:06,270
Eastern Inspection Division,

330
00:16:06,270 --> 00:16:09,080
overseeing martial matters
within the Great Xia,

331
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:11,510
supervising the MAA,

332
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:13,480
and monitoring government officials.

333
00:16:13,670 --> 00:16:16,320
He is granted the right
to report directly to the throne.

334
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,870
Thus decreed.

335
00:16:17,870 --> 00:16:21,840
Long live His Majesty!

336
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,000
Wu Guangming!

337
00:16:29,630 --> 00:16:31,200
You traitor!

338
00:16:31,750 --> 00:16:33,270
