339
00:16:35,270 --> 00:16:36,200
Deng Yunfeng,

340
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:38,240
you and Eunuch Deng

341
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:40,550
have conspired with the Demonic Sect.

342
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:42,000
The evidence is clear.

343
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,630
Your qualification is revoked.

344
00:16:43,630 --> 00:16:45,030
Take him away!

345
00:16:45,550 --> 00:16:46,390
Yes!

346
00:16:49,270 --> 00:16:50,240
Gou Lingfeng,

347
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:51,240
