355
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:06,720
Gou Lingfeng!

356
00:17:07,360 --> 00:17:08,630
Wake up!

357
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:11,440
Gou Lingfeng!

358
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:18,080
Lingfeng,

359
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,640
congratulations.

360
00:17:20,310 --> 00:17:22,790
