365
00:17:31,750 --> 00:17:34,030
Success is what matters most.

366
00:17:34,510 --> 00:17:35,960
Here, take it.

367
00:17:36,780 --> 00:17:38,700
(Hero)

368
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:50,920
I now declare,

369
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:52,640
from this day forth,

370
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:54,440
Gou Lingfeng

371
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:58,110
shall be the next Chairman of the MAA.

372
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:00,400
He will work closely with me

373
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,830
to safeguard

374
00:18:02,550 --> 00:18:05,350
the peace of Great Xia's martial world.

375
00:18:08,790 --> 00:18:10,030
This moment

376
00:18:10,310 --> 00:18:11,350
belongs to you.

377
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:13,240
Go ahead.

378
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:21,350
Fellow martial artists,

379
00:18:22,030 --> 00:18:23,160
I never imagined

380
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:26,030
that I would one day stand here

381
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:28,400
as Chairman of the MAA.

382
00:18:29,350 --> 00:18:31,400
Ever since I was a kid, I had a dream,

383
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,510
that was to become a great hero.

384
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,640
But I wasn't good-looking,

385
00:18:36,070 --> 00:18:38,640
and was often mistaken
for a Demonic Sect member.

386
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:42,200
Even so, I never gave up on that dream.

387
00:18:42,590 --> 00:18:43,680
Because I knew

388
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:45,550
what truly matters

389
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,200
is the heroism in your heart.

390
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:50,510
Achieving this dream

391
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:51,880
would've been impossible

392
00:18:52,790 --> 00:18:53,880
without my companions,

393
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:56,270
without my master,

394
00:18:58,270 --> 00:19:00,550
and without

395
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:03,720
Chairman Wu's support

396
00:19:04,270 --> 00:19:05,680
every step

397
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,070
of the way.

398
00:19:09,750 --> 00:19:11,440
Today's success

399
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:13,510
isn't mine alone.

400
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:15,550
It belongs to all of us.

401
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:17,070
Let's work together

402
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:20,440
to build a peaceful

403
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:21,720
and brand new martial world.

404
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:24,640
We mustn't let doubts
and misunderstandings

405
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,640
cloud our path.

406
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:28,590
Let righteousness and justice

407
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:31,200
become our only goal.

408
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:34,550
Divine Sect! Divine Sect! Divine Sect!

409
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:37,510
Glory to the Sect Chief!

410
00:19:37,510 --> 00:19:38,830
Why are you all here?

411
00:19:40,270 --> 00:19:41,350
Greetings, Sect Chief.

412
00:19:41,550 --> 00:19:43,000
You're the Chairman now.

413
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:44,030
Reviving the Divine Sect

414
00:19:44,030 --> 00:19:45,510
is finally within reach.

415
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:47,400
Why are all of you here?

416
00:19:47,830 --> 00:19:48,830
It was the Sect Chief,

417
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:51,400
no, former chief Liu Guang, who sent us.

418
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:53,310
The Hero Gathering of the MAA

419
00:19:53,510 --> 00:19:54,880
is about to begin.

420
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:56,440
If nothing goes wrong,

421
00:19:56,790 --> 00:19:59,030
Gou Lingfeng will win

422
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:00,790
and become the new Chairman

423
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,720
of the MAA.

424
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:03,880
When the time comes,

425
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:06,270
you guys go in disguise,

426
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:07,680
blend into the crowd,

427
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,550
and when Gou Lingfeng

428
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:11,590
ascended to the presidency,

429
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:14,070
you must fully support him

430
00:20:14,270 --> 00:20:15,590
in becoming the new Sect Chief

431
00:20:16,510 --> 00:20:17,830
and reviving the Divine Sect.

432
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:19,030
Liu Guang?

433
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:20,720
That's impossible.

434
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,270
His prediction was spot-on.

435
00:20:23,830 --> 00:20:24,790
We've been oppressed

436
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:25,920
by the MAA for so long.

437
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:27,160
Now, finally,

438
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:28,680
we can live in peace again.

439
00:20:29,350 --> 00:20:30,550
Revive the Divine Sect!

440
00:20:30,750 --> 00:20:33,310
Revive the Divine Sect!

441
00:20:33,310 --> 00:20:34,440
They're the Demonic Sect!

442
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:37,270
Gou Lingfeng is their leader!

443
00:20:38,030 --> 00:20:38,870
Chairman,

444
00:20:39,070 --> 00:20:40,000
I'm not!

445
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:42,640
The battle between good and evil

446
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:44,030
has raged for centuries.

447
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:45,350
But evil

448
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:46,830
can never triumph over justice.

449
00:20:48,270 --> 00:20:49,110
Gou Lingfeng,

450
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:51,590
as Chairman of the MAA,

451
00:20:51,790 --> 00:20:53,590
you must eliminate them all.

452
00:20:59,270 --> 00:21:01,400
What's going on here, General Wu?

453
00:21:05,860 --> 00:21:06,730
Lingfeng,

454
00:21:07,090 --> 00:21:09,090
I've watched you come this far.

455
00:21:09,090 --> 00:21:11,070
I know your character
better than anyone.

456
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:12,830
But these remnants of the Demonic Sect

457
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:14,550
just called you "Sect Chief"

458
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:15,750
in front of everyone.

459
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:17,350
