460
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,750
So you must kill them.

461
00:21:20,070 --> 00:21:21,270
It's the only way

462
00:21:21,270 --> 00:21:23,070
to clear yourself of suspicion.

463
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:24,830
He's right, Gou Lingfeng!

464
00:21:24,830 --> 00:21:26,310
Hurry up and do it!

465
00:21:28,030 --> 00:21:28,870
Wait,

466
00:21:29,070 --> 00:21:30,720
but we didn't do anything!

467
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:31,830
Chief Gou,

468
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:33,400
