478
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:48,350
Floral Knight,

479
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:50,310
they're standing here shouting about

480
00:21:50,310 --> 00:21:51,550
"reviving the Divine Sect",

481
00:21:51,790 --> 00:21:54,200
do they really seem like
ordinary villagers?

482
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:56,270
Chairman,

483
00:21:56,270 --> 00:21:58,160
there must be some
misunderstanding here.

484
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,080
Lingfeng,

485
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:02,510
you've come such a long way,

486
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:04,510
you know best what it took.

487
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,550
Your heart is righteous,

488
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:09,160
yet you've constantly been mistaken,

489
00:22:09,160 --> 00:22:10,550
mistreated and scorned.

490
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:13,480
Don't you feel even a little resentment?

491
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:17,440
Now's your chance to prove yourself,

492
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:19,590
and your best chance to offer
a token of loyalty

493
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:21,240
as the new Chairman of the MAA.

494
00:22:26,640 --> 00:22:27,480
Lingfeng.

495
00:22:31,310 --> 00:22:32,200
Chairman,

496
00:22:32,440 --> 00:22:33,350
these people

497
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:34,960
can't be killed.

498
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:36,800
Lingfeng,

499
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:39,680
these people are notorious

500
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:42,030
throughout the martial world.

501
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,640
Killing them is justice.

502
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,310
After this,

503
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:47,880
no more Demonic Sect.

504
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,590
That'll bring peace.

505
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:53,110
No!

506
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,000
Lingfeng,

507
00:22:58,790 --> 00:23:00,640
if you don't have the heart to do it,

508
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:02,720
I'll do it for you.

509
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:03,560
Stop!

510
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:07,720
They're just innocent civilians!

511
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:09,270
They are survivors

512
00:23:09,480 --> 00:23:11,270
of that great tragedy years ago.

513
00:23:11,270 --> 00:23:12,790
They've suffered so much

514
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:15,640
just trying to find a peaceful home.

515
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:18,550
My master may seem greedy,

516
00:23:19,070 --> 00:23:20,030
but he used all his money

517
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:22,110
to take care of these people.

518
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:25,270
