519
00:23:25,790 --> 00:23:27,640
They've done nothing wrong.

520
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,720
They only came here

521
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:32,400
because Liu Guang deceived them.

522
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:35,110
