523
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:36,590
and use their lives

524
00:23:36,590 --> 00:23:38,200
to build my reputation?

525
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:40,160
Is that fair?

526
00:23:40,170 --> 00:23:41,180
Gou Lingfeng,

527
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:43,240
don't throw away your future.

528
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:45,400
The kind of hero I want to be

529
00:23:46,510 --> 00:23:47,960
isn't this kind.

530
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:49,310
Gou Lingfeng!

531
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:54,240
If

532
00:23:54,750 --> 00:23:56,000
I have to do these things

533
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:58,830
just to be Chairman of the MAA,

534
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:02,590
then I don't want

535
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:04,860
this Hero Token.

536
00:24:04,860 --> 00:24:05,740
(Hero)

537
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,960
The Divine Sect robe?

538
00:24:22,270 --> 00:24:23,830
Ever since I learned my master

539
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:25,310
taught me demonic techniques,

540
00:24:26,030 --> 00:24:27,720
