543
00:24:33,830 --> 00:24:34,790
Gou Lingfeng,

544
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:38,110
you've disappointed me deeply.

545
00:24:41,310 --> 00:24:42,680
The bright sky has perished.

546
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:44,350
The long night is coming.

547
00:24:45,160 --> 00:24:46,680
I shall follow my path

548
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:49,160
to embrace the new beginning.

549
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:50,310
I, Gou Lingfeng, hereby

550
00:24:50,640 --> 00:24:54,070
assume the title of Chief
of the Great Evolution.

551
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,510
I ask all members of the sect

552
00:24:56,750 --> 00:24:58,200
to stand united.

553
00:24:58,200 --> 00:25:00,310
We will not kill the innocent.

554
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,640
But we will not

555
00:25:03,350 --> 00:25:04,720
allow ourselves to be trampled.

556
00:25:05,310 --> 00:25:06,830
Great Evolution stands forever.

557
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:08,920
The sacred flame burns eternal.

558
00:25:09,350 --> 00:25:11,200
May the Sect Chief's glory

559
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:13,070
shine through the ages.

560
00:25:13,070 --> 00:25:14,270
We pledge ourselves

561
00:25:14,270 --> 00:25:16,270
to our Sect Chief!

562
00:25:16,270 --> 00:25:18,000
Silence, all of you!

563
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:23,400
I am Wu Guangming,

564
00:25:24,110 --> 00:25:25,790
General of Bandit Suppression

565
00:25:26,070 --> 00:25:27,240
and Officer of the EID!

566
00:25:28,110 --> 00:25:29,110
Guards!

567
00:25:29,110 --> 00:25:29,950
Here!

568
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:32,350
Kill them all.

569
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:34,240
Leave no one alive.

570
00:25:35,240 --> 00:25:36,080
No!

571
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,000
Sect Chief!

572
00:25:58,240 --> 00:25:59,080
Hu San'er!

573
00:25:59,310 --> 00:26:00,150
Hu San'er!

574
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:04,590
Sect Chief...

575
00:26:05,660 --> 00:26:08,070
He... he's a bad man.

576
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:11,880
You...

577
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:14,590
You have to protect everyone.

578
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:17,000
We just want...

579
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:19,310
We just want to live in peace.

580
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:22,520
We all

581
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:25,110
believe in you...

582
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:27,520
Hu San'er!

583
00:26:28,590 --> 00:26:29,430
Hu San'er!

584
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:41,110
Master!

585
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:44,560
Grandpa!

586
00:26:45,310 --> 00:26:46,590
Grandpa, I'm here!

587
00:26:59,550 --> 00:27:00,390
Ling'er!

588
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:04,320
Ling'er!

589
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:05,520
Are you okay?

590
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,640
Ling'er, are you alright?

591
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:35,200
Heng,

592
00:27:35,590 --> 00:27:36,550
I'm sorry.

593
00:27:36,790 --> 00:27:38,160
It's my fault.

594
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:40,790
I thought

595
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:42,680
I could protect you all.

596
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:45,030
Yingdan and Mr. Gou

597
00:27:45,030 --> 00:27:46,510
treated me like family,

598
00:27:46,920 --> 00:27:48,640
but I ended up hurting everyone.

599
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:49,840
And me?

600
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:51,560
Ling'er,

601
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:56,070
what about us?

602
00:27:57,510 --> 00:27:58,960
Was it real or not?

603
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:00,240
It was real.

604
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:01,720
All of it was real, Heng.

605
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:05,070
This whole time,

606
00:28:05,310 --> 00:28:06,680
I was torn.

607
00:28:07,310 --> 00:28:08,240
I thought,

608
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:10,750
my godfather would never hurt you,

609
00:28:11,070 --> 00:28:13,350
but something felt wrong.

610
00:28:13,790 --> 00:28:14,720
I kept debating

611
00:28:14,720 --> 00:28:16,590
whether to tell you everything,

612
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,040
but

613
00:28:18,270 --> 00:28:20,720
I didn't dare defy his orders.

614
00:28:21,510 --> 00:28:22,350
Godfather?

615
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:25,680
Wu Guangming is your godfather?

616
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:31,200
When Father and I first came
to Huizhou City,

617
00:28:32,550 --> 00:28:34,070
it was hard to make a living

618
00:28:34,070 --> 00:28:35,550
just the two of us.

619
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,310
He helped us

620
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:39,750
open the Beauty Salon

621
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:42,790
and asked martial artists
to look after our business.

622
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:44,350
That's how we survived.

623
00:28:44,830 --> 00:28:45,750
He...

624
00:28:46,270 --> 00:28:47,830
he's our benefactor.

625
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:49,400
I understand now.

626
00:28:50,270 --> 00:28:51,750
No wonder He Changzai kept urging

627
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:53,880
my master and me to get our faces done.

628
00:28:57,350 --> 00:28:59,240
I've always been sickly since childhood.

629
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:01,750
No one wanted to play with me.

630
00:29:02,830 --> 00:29:03,790
I thought

631
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:07,200
if I was more obedient,

632
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:08,720
more useful,

633
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:10,640
then maybe people would accept me.

634
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:13,440
But after meeting all of you,

635
00:29:13,720 --> 00:29:15,070
you treated me like family.

636
00:29:15,070 --> 00:29:16,640
Especially you, Heng.

637
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:19,030
Ever since I first saw you,

638
00:29:19,030 --> 00:29:20,590
I liked you.

639
00:29:22,070 --> 00:29:23,480
But now,

640
00:29:24,070 --> 00:29:25,830
I've let everyone down.

641
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:28,480
Silly girl,

642
00:29:31,510 --> 00:29:32,550
I believe you.

643
00:29:34,400 --> 00:29:35,240
I believe

644
00:29:36,720 --> 00:29:37,560
my master

645
00:29:37,750 --> 00:29:38,880
and Yingdan

646
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:40,590
would not blame you either.

647
00:29:42,830 --> 00:29:43,790
Really?

648
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:45,480
Really.

649
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:52,960
But I hope

650
00:29:53,590 --> 00:29:54,830
you'll believe in me too.

651
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:57,000
Whatever happens, tell me.

652
00:29:57,960 --> 00:29:59,200
Let's face it together.

653
00:29:59,590 --> 00:30:00,430
Alright?

654
00:30:08,310 --> 00:30:09,160
Silly girl.

655
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:26,520
Grandpa?

656
00:30:27,520 --> 00:30:28,400
Let's go.

657
00:30:28,400 --> 00:30:29,240
Retreat! Retreat!

658
00:30:32,480 --> 00:30:33,790
Even though I don't like you,

659
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:34,830
I can't stand watching

660
00:30:34,830 --> 00:30:36,200
that guy slaughter innocent people

661
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:37,400
on my father's land.

662
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:39,840
Girl,

663
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:41,270
you're smart.

664
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:42,440
If not for you,

665
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:43,400
my grandson wouldn't have

666
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:44,550
made it out alive tonight.

667
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,270
It's all because of him.

668
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:54,280
Wu Guangming!

669
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:56,270
You tried to silence everyone!

670
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:58,680
Linglong, stop talking nonsense.

671
00:30:58,680 --> 00:30:59,920
The situation is settled.

672
00:30:59,920 --> 00:31:02,240
You... you better not act rashly.

673
00:31:03,270 --> 00:31:04,110
Father,

674
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,680
your way of dealing with people

675
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:08,030
doesn't work on Wu Guangming.

676
00:31:08,030 --> 00:31:09,310
Just sit back and watch.

677
00:31:09,310 --> 00:31:10,200
Trust me.

678
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:11,040
Be good.

679
00:31:14,550 --> 00:31:15,510
Back when

680
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:16,590
Wang Zipeng and I

681
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:18,070
were investigating
the Puppet Knight case,

682
00:31:18,070 --> 00:31:19,110
we discovered He Changzai

683
00:31:19,110 --> 00:31:20,790
was acting under Wu Guangming's orders.

684
00:31:20,790 --> 00:31:22,030
That's why he was so desperate

685
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:24,750
to execute the Puppet Knight
on the spot.

686
00:31:25,310 --> 00:31:26,200
I knew then

687
00:31:26,200 --> 00:31:28,030
your identity was suspicious.

688
00:31:28,350 --> 00:31:29,750
And after digging deeper,

689
00:31:29,750 --> 00:31:31,200
just as I suspected,

690
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:32,750
behind it all

691
00:31:32,750 --> 00:31:34,640
was Wu Guangming.

692
00:31:36,310 --> 00:31:37,150
No,

693
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:39,790
the former leader of the Demonic Sect,

694
00:31:40,030 --> 00:31:40,960
Liu Guang!

695
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,080
Liu Guang!

696
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:51,480
You hypocritical monster!

697
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:52,330
Self-righteous fraud!

698
00:31:52,340 --> 00:31:53,240
You dared lecture me?

699
00:31:53,240 --> 00:31:54,350
You're finished.

700
00:31:54,350 --> 00:31:55,510
I'm writing ten exposés on you!

701
00:31:55,510 --> 00:31:56,750
You're done for.

702
00:31:57,590 --> 00:31:58,790
Your name will live in infamy forever.

703
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,000
You're finished.

704
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:02,200
- Godfather!
- Ling'er!

705
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:05,480
Why would you do this to us?

706
00:32:07,030 --> 00:32:08,000
Godfather!

707
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,070
Why?

708
00:32:10,830 --> 00:32:11,830
Gou Lingfeng,

709
00:32:12,070 --> 00:32:13,270
did you hear that?

710
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,240
She called me "Godfather."

711
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:19,270
Then why are you doing this to me?

712
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:23,030
If I hadn't taken you two in,

713
00:32:23,270 --> 00:32:25,790
you and your father would've
starved to death.

714
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:28,590
I treated you as my daughter,

715
00:32:28,830 --> 00:32:30,270
raised you with care,

716
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:32,030
fed and clothed you.

717
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:36,070
And now, you

718
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:38,240
want to run away?

719
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:40,270
If you stand in my way,

720
00:32:41,070 --> 00:32:43,070
then you'll have to die.

721
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:44,750
You jerk!

722
00:32:44,750 --> 00:32:46,000
I really regret

723
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:48,750
being soft-hearted back then.

724
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:52,350
I should've had that Puppet Knight
die with you!

725
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:53,310
You monster!

726
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:56,160
Ling'er treated you
like her real father,

727
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:57,960
followed your every word,

728
00:32:59,000 --> 00:33:01,160
and you just used her like a pawn,

729
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:02,920
then threw her away!

730
00:33:03,110 --> 00:33:05,550
Who in this world isn't a pawn?

731
00:33:07,590 --> 00:33:09,160
I used her

732
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:11,480
because she was still useful.

733
00:33:14,110 --> 00:33:15,510
But some people

734
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:18,480
are pawns and don't even know it.

735
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:19,750
How pathetic is that?

736
00:33:22,310 --> 00:33:23,150
Guards!

737
00:33:23,480 --> 00:33:24,320
- Here!
- Here!

738
00:33:25,070 --> 00:33:26,240
Bring Lord Deng over.

739
00:33:26,590 --> 00:33:27,430
- Yes!
- Yes!

740
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:29,510
Zhuge,

741
00:33:30,030 --> 00:33:33,000
you should really be thanking me.

742
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:34,680
If it weren't for me,

743
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:38,240
how could you two
have ended up together?

744
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,030
Liu Guang,

745
00:33:40,790 --> 00:33:42,030
so it was you!

746
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:44,070
It was always you.

747
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:46,110
You wore a mask

748
00:33:46,110 --> 00:33:47,720
for over twenty years.

749
00:33:48,240 --> 00:33:50,000
Do you even remember who you are?

750
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:53,920
You could even harm your own people!

751
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:56,640
You're worse than a beast!

752
00:33:57,510 --> 00:33:58,350
Liu Guang,

753
00:33:58,790 --> 00:34:01,270
I know you're not who you used to be,

754
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:03,550
but I never thought,

755
00:34:03,550 --> 00:34:05,590
you'd hide this deep.

756
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:08,640
You really saw all of us

757
00:34:08,640 --> 00:34:11,000
as pieces on your chessboard.

758
00:34:11,240 --> 00:34:12,270
These people

759
00:34:12,270 --> 00:34:14,830
once fought and bled at your side,

760
00:34:15,200 --> 00:34:17,830
yet you had no mercy slaughtering them?

761
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:22,760
Yingdan.

762
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,120
Yingdan.

763
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:28,200
Liu Guang,

764
00:34:29,920 --> 00:34:31,840
so you always knew?

765
00:34:32,590 --> 00:34:33,800
You knew I was in the MAA

766
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:35,800
and that my mother and I existed?

767
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:37,200
Yingdan,

768
00:34:38,110 --> 00:34:39,070
believe me.

769
00:34:39,070 --> 00:34:40,150
Trust your father.

770
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:42,110
Once this is all over,

771
00:34:42,480 --> 00:34:44,710
I'll make it up to you
and your mother tenfold.

772
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:47,710
You're not fit to be my father.

773
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:49,670
You're not even fit to be
my mother's husband.

774
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,680
Yingdan,

775
00:34:51,710 --> 00:34:53,280
I had no choice.

776
00:34:57,280 --> 00:34:58,840
That night,

777
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,630
our Divine Sect was destroyed.

778
00:35:03,110 --> 00:35:05,510
Do you know what it's like

779
00:35:05,510 --> 00:35:06,710
to watch your closest loved ones,

780
00:35:06,710 --> 00:35:08,190
your dearest friends,

781
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:11,510
die in front of you?

782
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:14,760
To protect you and your mother,

783
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:18,480
I had to change identities
and hide away,

784
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:20,550
waiting for the right time
to rise again.

785
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:25,480
You may not understand now,

786
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:29,110
but one day,

787
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:32,670
you will.

788
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:36,070
- Let me go!
- Gou Lingfeng!

789
00:35:36,550 --> 00:35:38,920
A bright future lies ahead for you.

790
00:35:39,550 --> 00:35:41,110
You like Yingdan, right?

791
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:43,550
I can marry her to you.

792
00:35:44,630 --> 00:35:45,920
From now on,

793
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:49,150
you and I can rule the martial world
together.

794
00:35:49,550 --> 00:35:51,440
Wouldn't that be grand?

795
00:35:51,880 --> 00:35:52,720
Gou Lingfeng!

796
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:54,670
You can't agree!

797
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:56,000
You can't!

798
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,630
If you do, it's over between us!

799
00:35:57,630 --> 00:35:58,510
Gou Lingfeng!

800
00:35:58,880 --> 00:35:59,760
Gou Lingfeng!

801
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:03,230
If you still stand by my side,

802
00:36:03,710 --> 00:36:05,150
everything

803
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:07,400
can be forgiven.

804
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:09,280
Otherwise,

805
00:36:10,510 --> 00:36:12,920
I'll make sure you're doomed eternally.

806
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:14,230
Mr. Gou!

807
00:36:14,230 --> 00:36:15,440
Don't believe him!

808
00:36:15,760 --> 00:36:17,590
He's been using me to deceive you!

809
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:21,840
This mask belonged to Liu Guang.

810
00:36:22,110 --> 00:36:24,630
My father asked me to give you
before he died.

811
00:36:24,630 --> 00:36:26,230
He wanted to tell you the truth.

812
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:28,920
But I was blinded by Wu Guangming

813
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:31,550
and hid it away.

814
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:34,360
I've wandered with Ling'er
for many years.

815
00:36:34,550 --> 00:36:36,030
This time, we may not escape.

816
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,590
Then tell me, back then,

817
00:36:37,590 --> 00:36:39,320
did you collude with the Demonic Sect?

818
00:36:39,710 --> 00:36:40,960
This world isn't as black-and-white

819
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:42,320
as you think.

820
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:44,710
What happened back then was complicated.

821
00:36:45,670 --> 00:36:47,710
So did you, or didn't you?

822
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:51,710
I only helped a wrong person.

823
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:55,110
Gou Lingfeng, think carefully.

824
00:36:55,320 --> 00:36:56,230
Gou Lingfeng!

825
00:36:57,960 --> 00:36:59,070
You cannot agree!

826
00:37:00,670 --> 00:37:02,000
Be the kind of hero you believe in!

827
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,920
I'll survive, don't worry about me!

828
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,880
- Yingdan!
- Yingdan!!

829
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:07,720
Yingdan!

830
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:08,760
You...

831
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:10,760
I've said it before,

832
00:37:11,230 --> 00:37:12,840
the kind of hero I want to be

833
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:15,070
isn't this kind.

834
00:37:15,590 --> 00:37:16,430
Ling'er.

835
00:37:20,150 --> 00:37:21,150
Thank you, my lady.

836
00:37:31,820 --> 00:37:35,380
(The End of Episode 29)

837
00:38:03,150 --> 00:38:03,990
Who's there?

838
00:38:05,230 --> 00:38:06,070
Old Sect Chief?

839
00:38:06,360 --> 00:38:07,200
Liu Guang.

840
00:38:08,960 --> 00:38:10,800
Why are you still here?

841
00:38:10,930 --> 00:38:11,800
Don't even ask.

842
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:12,880
I got drunk last night

843
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:14,150
and passed out here!

844
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:15,000
What...

845
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,550
What's going on out there?

846
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,120
Old Sect Chief,

847
00:38:19,510 --> 00:38:20,360
listen to me.

848
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:22,280
You stay right here,

849
00:38:22,550 --> 00:38:24,230
don't come out until everything's

850
00:38:24,230 --> 00:38:25,280
quiet out there.

851
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:26,150
Then what about you?

852
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:27,880
Don't worry about me.

853
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:29,800
I'm going down with the ship!

854
00:38:34,150 --> 00:38:35,000
Old Sect Chief,

855
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:37,710
the revival of the Divine Sect

856
00:38:39,110 --> 00:38:40,550
will be your mission.

